(Aoi) Excuse me...

490
00:36:25,933 --> 00:36:28,933
(Aoi) Ah... Kozue-chan.

491
00:36:28,933 --> 00:36:30,933
I came to deliver that package...

492
00:36:30,933 --> 00:36:35,933
Ah, I was transferred to the General Affairs Department.

493
00:36:35,933 --> 00:36:39,933
Please here. (Aoi) Yeah.

494
00:36:39,933 --> 00:36:44,933
Was that what Aoi-san wanted? Go to the General Affairs Department.

495
00:36:44,933 --> 00:36:46,933
Huh?

496
00:36:46,933 --> 00:36:49,933
I guess I gave up again.

497
00:36:54,933 --> 00:36:57,933
(Aoi) 《I gave up on my dream》

498
00:37:00,933 --> 00:37:05,933
(Okuda) 《I can't believe I just can't understand the scent of flowers.》

499
00:37:05,933 --> 00:37:10,933
(Aoi) 《That's why I didn't want to give up on Yuko》➡

500
00:37:10,933 --> 00:37:12,933
《But...》

501
00:37:15,933 --> 00:37:17,933
(mobile phone)

502
00:37:25,933 --> 00:37:27,933
Huh?

503
00:37:29,933 --> 00:37:38,933
(Mobile phone) (Vibrator sound)

504
00:37:38,933 --> 00:37:40,933
(clicks tongue)

505
00:37:44,933 --> 00:37:46,933
(Masumi) Around here?

506
00:37:48,933 --> 00:37:50,933
Ah, Sumiharu.

507
00:38:31,933 --> 00:38:33,933
Thank you for coming.

508
00:38:33,933 --> 00:38:35,933
I'm sorry all of a sudden.

509
00:38:35,933 --> 00:38:39,933
Ah... that… .

510
00:38:39,933 --> 00:38:42,933
happy birthday .

511
00:38:42,933 --> 00:38:44,933
Huh?

512
00:38:51,933 --> 00:38:55,933
Was it wrong? (Aoi) No...

513
00:38:55,933 --> 00:38:58,933
Why?

514
00:38:58,933 --> 00:39:00,933
this .

515
00:39:00,933 --> 00:39:02,933
Huh? (Sumiharu) You dropped it, right?

516
00:39:02,933 --> 00:39:05,933
In front of the concourse peony painting at the station.

517
00:39:05,933 --> 00:39:10,933
(Aoi) 《Ah…. Oh, I'm sorry...》 (Male) 《Excuse me》

518
00:39:10,933 --> 00:39:13,933
(Aoi) 《Hmm... Huh…》

519
00:39:13,933 --> 00:39:15,933
《Ah》

520
00:39:17,933 --> 00:39:19,933
Ah!

521
00:39:21,933 --> 00:39:25,933
I thought you might like peony.

522
00:39:39,933 --> 00:39:43,933
I like that picture.

523
00:39:43,933 --> 00:39:45,933
Eh...

524
00:39:45,933 --> 00:39:48,933
Lively➡

525
00:39:48,933 --> 00:39:51,933
I can almost smell it➡

526
00:39:51,933 --> 00:39:56,933
Because it reminds me of happy feelings. ➡

527
00:39:56,933 --> 00:39:59,933
No matter how hard it is.

528
00:40:03,933 --> 00:40:06,933
Ah... I'm sorry. I… .

529
00:40:06,933 --> 00:40:08,933
Ah, no.

530
00:40:18,933 --> 00:40:22,933
Well then. I really wanted to give you this.

531
00:40:22,933 --> 00:40:26,933
happy birthday… . ⚟ (Masumi) What are you doing?

532
00:40:26,933 --> 00:40:29,933
I can't believe it at a time like this. ➡

533
00:40:29,933 --> 00:40:31,933
You have something to say to me.

534
00:40:31,933 --> 00:40:34,933
What do you mean by just shutting up and doing whatever you want? ➡

535
00:40:34,933 --> 00:40:36,933
Hey, let's go. I'm going to cancel it now.

536
00:40:36,933 --> 00:40:39,933
What a settlement! (Sumiharu) Stop it.

537
00:40:39,933 --> 00:40:41,933
Hey, let's go, hey!

538
00:40:41,933 --> 00:40:43,933
(Sumiharu) Huh! Hmm... hmm! (Masumi) What is it? ➡

539
00:40:43,933 --> 00:40:45,933
Hey, let's go! Hey! Come on!

540
00:40:45,933 --> 00:40:47,933
(Aoi) Hey! Please let go. (Masumi) Oh?

541
00:40:47,933 --> 00:40:49,933
Oh? What are you?

542
00:40:49,933 --> 00:40:51,933
You might be injured.

543
00:40:51,933 --> 00:40:53,933
It's noisy. This is no big deal.

544
00:40:53,933 --> 00:40:56,933
It's not up to you to decide, right?

545
00:40:56,933 --> 00:40:59,933
It's up to me to decide!

546
00:40:59,933 --> 00:41:02,933
Ah! (Masumi) Don't let anyone who has nothing to do with it say anything.

547
00:41:08,933 --> 00:41:11,933
(sound of trampling on a bouquet)

548
00:41:11,933 --> 00:41:13,933
(Masumi) Ah... Ah! (sound of trampling on a bouquet)

549
00:41:13,933 --> 00:41:15,933
Please stop. (Masumi) Don't disturb me. What is it...? ➡

550
00:41:15,933 --> 00:41:18,933
Huh? Even though you don't know anything, you say such big things! ➡

551
00:41:18,933 --> 00:41:21,933
Don't be fooled by treating people like the bad guys!

552
00:41:21,933 --> 00:41:24,933
let's go .

553
00:41:24,933 --> 00:41:26,933
(Masumi) Wait.

554
00:41:26,933 --> 00:41:28,933
Sunny weather!

555
00:41:37,933 --> 00:41:43,933
(Aoi) 《Fresh and refreshing, sweet and transparent》➡

556
00:41:43,933 --> 00:41:50,933
《The scent of peony brings faint expectations for summer》➡

557
00:41:50,933 --> 00:41:55,933
《It’s a feeling of happiness that can only be found in this season》➡

558
00:41:55,933 --> 00:42:03,933
《Maybe this period, before I know the reality, is the happiest》➡

559
00:42:03,933 --> 00:42:09,933
《Summer, love, dreams...》

560
00:42:09,933 --> 00:42:12,933
(Aoi) Ah, stop, stop, stop... ➡

561
00:42:12,933 --> 00:42:14,933
Ah, I can't do it anymore! Ah...

562
00:42:14,933 --> 00:42:18,933
(Sumiharu) Sorry. Um, are you okay?

563
00:42:18,933 --> 00:42:20,933
(Aoi) I'm fine... ➡

564
00:42:20,933 --> 00:42:24,933
But you don't seem to be okay.

565
00:42:24,933 --> 00:42:26,933
Eh...

566
00:42:26,933 --> 00:42:32,933
You've been looking sad ever since.

567
00:42:48,933 --> 00:42:50,933
Hmm...

568
00:42:50,933 --> 00:42:52,933
Huh...

569
00:43:04,933 --> 00:43:08,933
Happy birthday Aoi-san.

570
00:43:12,933 --> 00:43:15,933
Ah...

571
00:43:15,933 --> 00:43:27,933
♬～

572
00:43:27,933 --> 00:43:31,933
♬～

573
00:43:31,933 --> 00:43:35,933
Thank you, Subaru-kun.

574
00:43:46,933 --> 00:43:50,933
Sumiharu~?

575
00:43:50,933 --> 00:43:53,933
What? Isn't there?

576
00:43:53,933 --> 00:44:13,933
♬～

577
00:44:13,933 --> 00:44:17,933
♬～

578
00:44:17,933 --> 00:44:20,933
Please excuse me.

579
00:44:20,933 --> 00:44:40,933
♬～

580
00:44:40,933 --> 00:44:49,933
♬～

581
00:44:49,933 --> 00:44:52,933
(Mobile phone) (Shutter sound)

582
00:45:01,933 --> 00:45:03,933
Huh...

583
00:45:03,933 --> 00:45:23,933
♬～

584
00:45:23,933 --> 00:45:26,933
♬～

585
00:45:26,933 --> 00:45:28,933
Eh...

586
00:45:36,933 --> 00:45:38,933
Sweet scent...

587
00:45:38,933 --> 00:45:40,933
Huh?

588
00:45:43,933 --> 00:45:45,933
(Aoi) 《I wonder why》➡

589
00:45:45,933 --> 00:45:52,933
《It’s like something important that I had given up on comes back to life➡

590
00:45:52,933 --> 00:45:56,933
I had a premonition of such a miracle.

591
00:46:08,933 --> 00:46:10,933
[From “Last Note”]

592
00:46:17,933 --> 00:46:19,933
